# 2015 Nepalese presidential election

Indirect presidential elections were held in Nepal on 28 October 2015. Bidya Devi Bhandari of the Communist Party of Nepal (Unified Marxistâ€“Leninist) was elected president, becoming Nepal's first female head of state.
